<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. The holotype of Goniurosaurus gollum sp. nov. (SYS r 002420) at its habitat: a barren limestone cave of Guangdong, China. Photograph by Shuo Qi." , "Figure 4. Comparisons of iris color with three closely related congeners A Goniurosaurus gollum sp. nov. (holotype, SYS r 002420) B Goniurosaurus varius (holotype, SYS r 002333) C Goniurosaurus yingdeensis (holotype SYSr 000504) D Goniurosaurus zhelongi (holotype, SYS r 000770). Photographs by Shuo Qi and Ying-Yong Wang." , "Figure 3. Type series of Goniurosaurus gollum sp. nov. A holotype, male, SYS r 002420 B paratype, male, SYS r 002421 C paratype, female, SYS r 002421; (1) dorsal view; (2) dorsal view of head; (3) ventral view of head; (4) close-up of the precloacal region, the Arabic number refer to the number of precloacal pores. Photographs by Shuo Qi." , "Figure 2. A The general aspect of the adult male holotype of Goniurosaurus gollum sp. nov. (SYS r 002420) in life B scalation and coloration characters of the head of the holotype. Photographs by Shuo Qi." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/474309" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/474308" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/474307" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/474306" .

